item.title: Super fighters game for free
item.description: During the game Super Fighters for free you have to control an orange Stickman who will fight with many enemies. You will have to perform spectacular tricks and destroy opponents attacking the hero from all sides. At first, it will be very easy to do this, but the further you advance, the stronger and faster your opponents become.
